@MrGreenTea I now have a working dependency provider for elm packages and projects. You can see how it's done and used with that example: https://github.com/mpizenberg/pubgrub-dependency-provider-elm/blob/master/examples/solve_deps.rs

And deeper integration into another tool like a test runner is also visible here: https://github.com/mpizenberg/elm-test-rs/blob/08a4dd5bfa89aadbbae7983ecbbaaa4aeb3a822d/src/deps.rs#L118
@Matthieu Pizenberg oh cool I'll take a look at it when I find the time. I'm currently busy so I did not continue work on python usage the last week but hope to return to it in January
